Based on the draft Consumer Privacy Bill of Rights, this establishes the chain:<br> STAKEHOLDERS -> CPBR -> Charter -> Privacy Policy ->  CONSUMER  <br>Iteration will establish:<br> CPBR <- Charter <<- Privacy Policy <<<-  CONSUMER<br>Interactive, distributed regulation.<br>It will also involve tying this in with requirements of other countries, US States, and specified industries.  Anything that affects what a company can or must do with information must be expressed for the company's own purposes, and probably should be expressed to their customers.